data.content:
noun
plural -ings
[count] :a printed list - usually + of
The book includes a listing of local restaurants.
b listings [plural] :a printed list of things that includes detailed information about them
The newspaper provides movie listings. [=information about where and when movies are being shown in theaters]
TV listings [=information about when and on what channel television programs will be shown]
job listings
[count] :something included in a list
The telephone listing is wrong. [=they listed the wrong telephone number]
[count] :the act of including something in a list or the state of being included in a list
The company is seeking a listing on the stock exchange. [=the company wants to be listed on the stock exchange]

Danh từ
sự lập danh sách, sự ghi vào danh sách
danh sách
